title: Match of the Day - 25th October 2014 - HDTV X264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD     
Date: Saturday 25th October 2014 
Time: 22:25 to 23:45 

Gary Lineker introduces highlights from six Premier League matches, as reigning champions Manchester City face West Ham in the lunchtime kick-off at the Etihad Stadium. City were utterly dominant against the Hammers last season, winning all four of their encounters. They easily won both league matches and also enjoyed a record breaking 9-0 aggregate victory in the League Cup semi-finals.
Elsewhere, Liverpool host Hull City at Anfield. The Tigers have never won a match away at the Reds and have let in 30 goals in nine previous visits. But they have a decent record against them in the Premier League, having only lost one of their last three encounters.
In the other matches Southampton entertain Stoke, Arsenal travel to Sunderland, West Brom play Crystal Palace and Swansea take on Leicester in the evening kick-off.
